    "en": {
      "title": "Sudden increase in fuel allowance",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The fuel allowance of all MPs has suddenly been increased by nearly two lakhs, according to parliamentary information.",
        "Thus, an additional amount of nearly two lakhs will be credited to the Member of Parliament in remote areas like Jaffna for fuel every month.",
        "The fuel allowance given to MPs was revised to the old fuel price till last June. Due to the economic crisis, payment based on increased fuel prices was stopped in the past on the order of former Finance Minister Mr. Basil Rajapaksa.",
        "Several MPs had requested the government authorities to adjust the allowance to the cost of new fuel in view of the economic crisis. The sources further informed that the fuel allowance has been increased in response to the demand.",
        "Due to the fuel problem, many MPs from faraway places came to Parliament very rarely."
      ],
